# Pueue

## Enqueue a task for execution

pueue add

## Display the current status of all tasks

pueue status

## Kill all tasks, clean up afterwards and reset EVERYTHING!

pueue reset

## Display the log output of finished tasks. Prints either all logs or only the logs of specified tasks

pueue log

##Follow the output of a currently running task. This command works like tail -f

pueue follow
